{
  "stem": "4967.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Before this, we used to walk 10 kilometers to another camp to have a bath where they used to spray or something to do with our clothing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But it didn't help much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But then when they built in our camp, outside our camp, two hundred meters, they used-- we used to have a shower, a hot shower.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they used to steam our clothes that we had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The blue and white striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this helped us a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Otherwise, we wouldn't survive a day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- the lice, they suck out your blood, and you die or you get diseased.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] while I was working in the camp, I had already a feeling it's, for me, not good to be in the camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It's not right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We are only four children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One, two, three, four.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Four children.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "As I say, I'm-- we were two from Lithuania, one from Hungary, and another one from somewhere, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So I-- so I spoke to my father, I should give up the job in the camp and go work outside the camp at [NON-ENGLISH] or maybe somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So he said, the best thing, maybe, would be for you-- you'll work with me, as my helper.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He'll speak to his German supervisor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And he spoke to the German supervisor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He said, all right, if he can manage to go into this-- to this marching out with-- with this particular unit, he's all right.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He can work here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But what happened, he didn't tell him that I was only 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "He thought, he thought electrician, 20.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But 14 years old, he didn't tell him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I couldn't give up my job so easily.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
